# Tailwind CSS built output. The compiled tailwind-output.css IS committed so a
# fresh clone / `docker compose up` renders styled without a Node toolchain or a
# build step (the Docker image is Python-only). Regenerate it with the build
# script when templates/classes change; the hashed variants stay ignored.
app/static/css/tailwind-output.*.css

